{
  "id": "69bd0e8b6d9fb593493199e4",
  "title": "師弟歓談:金子みすゞ",
  "created": 1773997708,
  "updated": 1773997719,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b6d9fb593493199e4",
      "text": "師弟歓談:金子みすゞ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096755a",
      "text": "放課後の教室。窓から差し込む夕陽が、机の上にやわらかく広がっている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997719
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096755d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096755e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096755f",
      "text": "「ねえけいこ先生、『[金子みすゞ]』ってさ、最近ちょいバズってるよね。教科書にも出てきたし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967560",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967561",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967562",
      "text": "「“バズっている”というのは、多くの人の関心を集めている、ということね。ええ、そうですね。金子みすゞは、とてもやさしい詩を書く方でしたよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967563",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967564",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967565",
      "text": "「やさしい詩って、なんかふわっとしてない？正直、ちょい眠くなる系かと思ってたんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967566",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967567",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967568",
      "text": "「そう感じるのも無理はありませんね。でも、その“やさしさ”の中に、とても深いまなざしがあるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967569",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756b",
      "text": "「深いまなざし？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756d",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756e",
      "text": "「ええ。たとえば、みすゞは人だけでなく、小さな生き物や見過ごされがちな存在にも、同じように心を寄せていました」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096756f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967570",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967571",
      "text": "「あー、なんか『みんなちがって、みんないい』ってやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967572",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967573",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967574",
      "text": "「よく知っていますね。その通りです。あの言葉には、違いを認め合う大切さが込められています」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967575",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967576",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967577",
      "text": "「でもさ、それってキレイごとっていうか…現実そんな甘くなくね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967578",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967579",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757a",
      "text": "「“甘くないのではないか”と言いたいのね。確かに現実は厳しいことも多いです。でも、だからこそ、そういう考え方が支えになることもあるのですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757d",
      "text": "「支え、かあ…。なんか理想論って感じするけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096757f",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967580",
      "text": "「理想というのは、すぐに叶わないからこそ意味があるのです。みすゞの詩は、『こうあれたらいい』という願いを、静かに伝えているのですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967581",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967582",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967583",
      "text": "「へえ…。なんか、ちょっと見方変わったかも」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967584",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967585",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967586",
      "text": "「それはよかった。ふーこさんは、どういう言葉に心が動きますか？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967587",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967588",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967589",
      "text": "「んー…なんか、ガツンとくるやつ？共感エグい、みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758b",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758c",
      "text": "「“とても共感できるもの”ということですね。みすゞの詩も、静かですが、読む人の心にそっと触れてくるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096758f",
      "text": "「静かに刺さるタイプってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967590",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967591",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967592",
      "text": "「ええ、その表現も素敵ですね。大きな声ではなく、小さな声で語りかけてくるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967593",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967594",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967595",
      "text": "「なんかさ、今の時代って大声のやつばっかじゃん？SNSとか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967596",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967597",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967598",
      "text": "「そうですね。だからこそ、みすゞのような静かな言葉が、かえって新鮮に感じられるのかもしれません」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b0000000000967599",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759b",
      "text": "「なるほどね〜。逆にレアってことか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759d",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759e",
      "text": "「“貴重である”とも言えますね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b000000000096759f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a1",
      "text": "「じゃあさ、先生的に一番グッとくるみすゞのポイントってどこ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a3",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a4",
      "text": "「そうですね…。やはり、“誰も見ていないものにも意味がある”と信じているところでしょうか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a7",
      "text": "「うわ、それちょいエモい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675a9",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675aa",
      "text": "「“心にしみる”という意味ですね。ええ、本当にそう思います」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675ac",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675ad",
      "text": "「なんかさ、自分が気づいてないだけで、いろんなものに意味あるのかもって思えてきたわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675af",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b0",
      "text": "「その気づきこそ、みすゞの詩が届けたかったものかもしれませんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b3",
      "text": "「…ちょっと詩、ちゃんと読んでみよっかな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b5",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b6",
      "text": "「ええ、ぜひ。きっと、ふーこさんなりの感じ方が見つかりますよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b8",
      "text": "夕陽が少しずつ沈み、教室は静かなオレンジ色に包まれていく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675b9",
      "text": "ふーこはスマートフォンを取り出し、「金子みすゞ」と検索した。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675ba",
      "text": "その横で、けいこ先生はやさしく微笑んでいた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997708,
      "updated": 1773997708
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0e8b00000000009675bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
